{"tid":1291800,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"回歸初心：不割蓆，不篤灰，不分化，不陳雲","createTime":"2019-07-07T04:54:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T04:17:53.000Z","uid":46849,"like":150,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"cd632d16c14c576cd20fb7f3048442179334efc3","tid":1291800,"uid":46849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T04:54:42.000Z","msg":"陳雲 = 分化大師<br />\n講到明拒絕團結<br />\n講到明要日日清算<br />\n畢生一事無成<br />\n預言無數次落空<br />\n習慣買兩邊<br />\n中左就吹噓<br />\n唔中就話玩膠<br />\n教徒自命清高<br />\n屌義士為樂<br />\n玩弄虛無縹緲政治術語<br />\n導致無謂口水戰內耗<br />\n對抗爭無實際貢獻<br />\n2016 敗選後日日咀咒香港<br />\n又狂屌香港人<br />\n自稱退出網路<br />\n亦話退出社運<br />\n言而無信<br />\n分化為樂<br />\n打手眾多<br />\n哪裡有陳雲<br />\n哪裡有分化<br />\n<br />\n再講一次<br />\n不割蓆，不篤灰，不分化，不陳雲<br />\n目前五大訴求無一實現<br />\n連階段勝利都談不上<br />\n邊個吹噓邀功<br />\n邊個就係鬼<br />\n講完"},{"pid":"00e759f2b2c1753468181bf1099248ec3ed08898","tid":1291800,"uid":12510,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T04:55:54.000Z","msg":"push<br />\n但係好似會make the stupid people famous"},{"pid":"62b9fa0bf7c782910cabe4a8a27c2f3a592d2c54","tid":1291800,"uid":46849,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"00e759f2b2c1753468181bf1099248ec3ed08898","tid":1291800,"uid":12510,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T04:55:54.000Z","msg":"push<br />\n但係好似會make the stupid people famous"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T04:57:06.000Z","msg":"佢本身有網路名氣<br />\n我識得有朋友不知情<br />\n俾佢呃左"},{"pid":"ed06ee20c9ee4c98bf4da1841dc2162ce7c7d975","tid":1291800,"uid":125680,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"00e759f2b2c1753468181bf1099248ec3ed08898","tid":1291800,"uid":12510,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T04:55:54.000Z","msg":"push<br />\n但係好似會make the stupid people famous"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T04:57:13.000Z","msg":"國師already famous la<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe678b81b0c4cb3154607177d524252dcf6f2502","tid":1291800,"uid":125680,"l